      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-iva        to   w-edt-iva-cod          .
           perform   edt-cod-iva-000      thru edt-cod-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing codice da sostituire                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      02                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<D"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-edt-iva-cie        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
