      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dcf-pfz-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se richiesta sostituzione              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dcf-pfz-sns    =    zero
                     go to acc-dcf-pfz-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura del tasto Pf1                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[1] "               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
