      *              * Se Pf1                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "[1] "
                     go to acc-dcf-pfz-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Subroutine di accettazione valore sostitu-  *
      *                  * tivo                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-dcf-pfz-sos-000  thru acc-dcf-pfz-sos-999    .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-key    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-dcf-pfz-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
